Parking Lot

This underground parking lot in fact doesn't really much look like a parking lot...
Anyway, you can shoot the lamps in the ceiling and hide in the shadows.
I made the lamps sparking and crashing down when you shoot it.

I can't fix one bug, or I don't really even know is it a bug but the helmet of CT shines in the dark, so it's much easier for terrorist to see enemy.
